{"tid":2217081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"包圍警總  警員被打爆痱滋案  裝修工暴動等罪共判囚4年","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T07:39:26.000Z","uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6ab989bc88bcaf4d525cc32e9c2ef84db9601d","tid":2217081,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551612-20200925.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551612-20200925.htm&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=19da9c65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551612-20200925.htm&h=c8383acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551612-20200925.htm</a><br />\n包圍警總警員被打爆痱滋案　裝修工暴動等罪共判囚4年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年6月26日包圍警察總部案，警員供稱受襲致痱滋爆裂，26歲被告裝修工人岑曉麟上星期四被裁定暴動罪及普通襲擊罪成，他早前又承認一項無合理因由而沒有按照法庭的指定歸押，今日在區域法院被判囚4年。<br />\n<br />\n法官上周裁決時表示，警員遇襲痱滋爆裂實屬十分輕微，甚至可以說是微不足道，控方原本提出檢控被告襲擊引致他人身體受傷罪，不符客觀證據。<br />\n<br />\n法官又提到，不得不承認處理本案案情有困難，因涉及暴動行為與以往案例有別，不是一般與警方對抗、掟磚、襲警等行為，或在同類案件中算是輕微，判刑需作多方面平衡。"},{"pid":"0d1d81eaa012b84f2810466a3ae77a794d8d371f","tid":2217081,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:35:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fe14ac6702618d86e467d72c46417ef56b48191","tid":2217081,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:35:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fffc56d6d31df72bfa323e1c0c8863acbc2fa9a","tid":2217081,"uid":28504,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"算少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6be22f801de1ada639e31a5311725250fbba60